    "text": "Sensi AI is transforming the way we protect our seniors.\n\nNo cameras. No invasion of privacy.\nJust smart, 24/7 audio-based insights that actually matter.\n\nIt can detect:\n• Fall indicators\n• Confusion or distress\n• Wandering or pacing\n• Sleep changes\n• Mobility decline\n• Irregular routines\n• Early warning signs that something isn’t right\n\nRight now, with caregiver shortages everywhere, Sensi AI gives families peace of mind and gives agencies the real-time information they need to respond faster and care smarter.\n\nIf you want meaningful support between caregiver visits, Sensi AI is the tool I recommend every family and agency should know about. 💛\nMessage me for details.\n\nJanice | Senior Living Educator & Advocate\nCommunity Services Liaison | Award-Winning Author\n📘 The Complete Guide to Assisted Living\n📍 Serving Central Florida Families\n📧 seniorliaisoncfl@gmail.com\n🌐 seniorliaisoncfl.com\n\n#SeniorCare #ElderCare #SeniorLiving #AssistedLiving #MemoryCare   ",
